videos.description: Aaron Wiggins gets back on defense and swats TJ Gibbs' shot out of bounds.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Wiggins tracks back to block Gibbs' shot) 2019/12/04

videos.headline: Wiggins tracks back to block Gibbs' shot

videos.description: Aaron Wiggins steps up on defense again with a chasedown block, this time on Prentiss Hubb.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Wiggins nearly smacks his head on the backboard for the block) 2019/12/04

videos.headline: Wiggins nearly smacks his head on the backboard for the block

videos.description: Eric Ayala deflects the pass on defense, then takes the pass from Jalen Smith and dunks it down in Rex Pflueger's face.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Ayala hammers one home with no regard for the rim) 2019/12/04

videos.headline: Ayala hammers one home with no regard for the rim

videos.description: Aaron Wiggins' shot is off the mark, but he dashes towards the rim and slams the putback dunk down.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Wiggins follows his own miss with a putback jam to end the half) 2019/12/04

videos.headline: Wiggins follows his own miss with a putback jam to end the half
